Contact name: {{ $json.contact_name }}
Message: """{{ $json.message_body }}"""

Return:
{
  "funnel_stage": one of ["New Enquiry","Contacted","Booked In","In Workshop","Quote Sent","Approved","Won","Lost","Rebooked","Unqualified", null],
  "opp_value_cents": integer or null,
  "contact_name": string or null
}

Rules:
- Inbound message with any content -> default to "New Enquiry" unless clearly later in funnel.
- "Booked In" requires explicit confirmed date/time.
- "Approved" requires explicit acceptance of a prior quote.
- "Quote Sent" only when an actual quote/price is sent outbound.
- "Lost" / "Won" only on explicit signal.
- If unsure -> null."
    }
  ]
}

